{"tid":1597230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(真心) 我想知咩叫兄弟爬山 各自修行","createTime":"2019-09-27T00:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T00:59:53.000Z","uid":187404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0db21e8ef68f31f0ebd5990f7519f0cc26d284","tid":1597230,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:52:33.000Z","msg":"今朝睇左d post不停話對話無用叫人下次唔好去<br />\n又話去係鬼<br />\n<br />\n其實今次支持運動有不同光譜既人，深黃，淺黃，中立，大家有唔同岡位，琴晚可以比和理非係全世界做文宣，效果未知，但值得一試。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山唔係各自為目標一齊行咩？<br />\n<br />\n即係前線自行決定策略永不割席，和理非盡方法做文宣要全球關注各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n點解未知效果就唔贊同，即係勇武唔衝點知效果。<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"36bae76ef2f71771b9eb87752625aa55ff9d760d","tid":1597230,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b2b89263b6c3ce047ed6f0165530ae29103707","tid":1597230,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"81df8e41d3486f1f62d2eb0c83aa49466e5ea64f","tid":1597230,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdd8b83acc6ae99e5d60ceadd988455c5b008ee","tid":1597230,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"<im